data.description: Affordable and charming 2.81-acre farmette!  Lots of options to realize your own vision of country living with two fenced pastures, a 3-stall barn with electricity and storage room, and a separate storage outbuilding (14x32).  The recently painted custom-built home is an open concept floor plan with volume ceilings, 2 bedrooms and a fully renovated bathroom with tile floors and deep soaking tub/shower combination.  The stainless-steel appliances: stove, microwave and dishwasher are all recent additions to the kitchen which also has a convenient pantry.   Easy access from the rear deck to mudroom/laundry.  The home is set back off the paved, state-maintained road and is a great spot, whether you are interested in keeping animals (horses, goats, sheep, chickens or a couple cows), tending gardens, or simply enjoying the views.   The property is within a 25-minute drive to Orange, Culpeper, Louisa and Lake Anna. This central location offers easy access to amenities, services, recreational activities, and the natural beauty of the surrounding areas, while still providing the privacy and serenity of a rural retreat.  Whether you have a passion for horseback riding, gardening, or simply enjoying the beauty of the countryside, this property offers the perfect blend of open space and practicality.  This is a wonderful opportunity for individuals or families seeking a countryside retreat!
